snippet.title: My desktop will be overcome with birds, and yours can be too.
snippet.description:
http://samperson.itch.io/meadow
Social distancing is hard. Being isolated is hard. So I made this for you.
Amazing music by Louie Zong, "clouds & their shadows": https://louiezong.bandcamp.com/track/clouds-their-shadows
Support projects like this at http://patreon.com/sammakesvr !


you're looking great today btw
